Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.90,0:01:30.49,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,‘completeness’
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.49,0:01:34.32,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}嗚呼　命の灯を掲げ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.70,0:01:39.04,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 欺いて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.04,0:01:44.21,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}KiLLKiSS judy.., KiLLKiSS jude.., KiLLKiSS juda.., 抱きしめて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.21,0:01:52.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H656570&}ねぇ　無防備だね　美しい戯れに　人は壊れてゆく
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}可笑しいわね
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.22,0:02:08.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H20105B&}そう　このまま　壊れて
